  "comment": "Kratos LED Tube RGBW in/outdoor use: The Kratos LED Tube features full RGBW color mixing, giving you complete control over your lighting environment. Each tube can be controlled individually, allowing you to create complex lighting setups quickly and easily. With its lightweight and durable design, the Kratos Tube LED set is perfect for on-the-go shoots and studio productions alike. There is a wide variety of special effects to choose from, you can create stunning visual effects for any project, from commercials to musical performances. Take your event or production to the next level with the Kratos LED Tube System!\n\n",
